X
</date>
the width, with 
<number box="[212,227,1930,1956]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" value="6.0">6</number>
distal setae, without setae on the ventral and dorsal margins, article 
<number box="[1050,1066,1930,1956]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" value="3.0">3</number>
, slightly falcate, length 
<date box="[1355,1391,1930,1956]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52">
<number box="[1355,1369,1930,1956]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" value="4.0">4</number>
X
</date>
the width, minutely setose, without setae on the dorsal margin, with two ventral and three apical setae. Maxilla 
<number box="[1413,1428,1970,1996]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" value="1.0">1</number>
, outer plate wide, with 
<number box="[412,440,2010,2036]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" value="11.0">11</number>
setal-teeth in an arrangement 
<number box="[791,805,2010,2036]" pageId="7" pageNumber="52" value="7.0">7</number>
